……本来就是这样啊","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":7,"motionName":"smile03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":7,"voiceId":"evenr54-08-031","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":7}],"windowDisplayName":"摩卡","body":"一直以来，我为了兰而所做的事情\n果然都是不对的吧","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":7,"motionName":"sad01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":7,"voiceId":"evenr54-08-032","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":23}],"windowDisplayName":"莉莎","body":"摩卡……","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":23,"motionName":"sad01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":23,"voiceId":"evenr54-08-033","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":7}],"windowDisplayName":"摩卡","body":"而且，我明明隐约察觉到了，兰比大家\n稍微走得更前一些，却没能说出来……","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":7,"motionName":"nf04","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":7,"voiceId":"evenr54-08-034","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":7}],"windowDisplayName":"摩卡","body":"可能我是觉得害怕吧。\n害怕大家和兰知道这件事","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":7,"motionName":"